column5: First off I would like to thank MattK for jumping on board when we were a guy short. Matt's post yesterday pretty much summed up the trip. The total for the week 1,044 fish. Had a great time with great guys. Bugs were terrible with a big Mayfly hatch in the middle of the week. Pike ate 12" perch Kevin and I with dinner....Doug with 24 1/2" WalleyeRich with shore lunch....Matt with RichMatt and Kevin by the nightly fire
Good stuff! Already knew you had a good trip, but it's always nice seeing the pic's.
